42
00:06:58,880 --> 00:06:59,840
Miss Lan.

43
00:07:01,760 --> 00:07:02,560
You...
know me?

44
00:07:03,600 --> 00:07:04,560
Of course.
You disappeared at that time,

45
00:07:05,360 --> 00:07:06,880
