61
00:07:54,680 --> 00:07:56,040
Don't you get it?

62
00:07:58,800 --> 00:08:00,000
I'm protecting you.

63
00:08:10,280 --> 00:08:12,200
My parents died on the day

64
00:08:12,360 --> 00:08:14,280
