I admit,

92
00:09:14,440 --> 00:09:15,760
I initially approached you

93
00:09:16,680 --> 00:09:18,640
because you were the sole heir of Lanhe.

94
00:09:21,280 --> 00:09:22,880
That's why on our wedding day,

95
00:09:24,080 --> 00:09:26,360
once you got the legal inheritance,

96
00:09:28,000 --> 00:09:29,240
