97
00:09:29,400 --> 00:09:30,200
No.

98
00:09:31,600 --> 00:09:33,080
But after getting to know you,

99
00:09:34,000 --> 00:09:34,680
I felt

100
00:09:34,680 --> 00:09:36,080
your kindness and gentleness.

101
00:09:37,640 --> 00:09:38,960
I truly fell in love with you.

102
00:09:43,880 --> 00:09:44,960
In that case,

103
00:09:46,240 --> 00:09:47,200
for me,

104
00:09:48,440 --> 00:09:49,680
