I've been too kind to you.

112
00:10:34,680 --> 00:10:35,680
What do you want?

113
00:10:37,080 --> 00:10:38,160
I can tell you everything.

114
00:10:39,560 --> 00:10:40,200
No need.

115
00:10:41,120 --> 00:10:42,000
